---
layout: base.njk
title: "About"
description: "About this series, who Christadelphians are, what we believe, and a short video overview."
permalink: /about/
mainClass: site-main--bright
# Optional: set to a YouTube video id (11 characters) to show an embedded overview.
youtubeVideoId: "IGbjT0MQ-Ew"
# Transcript link under the video: either set transcriptSlug (matches src/transcripts/{{ slug }}.md permalink) or set transcriptUrl to a full path.
transcriptSlug: "about-overview"
# transcriptUrl: "/transcripts/custom-path/"
---

<div class="page-header page-header--bright">
  About The Christadelphians
  <div class="container bright-section about-intro">
    <p class="bright-lead">
      This site supports a series of Bible presentations. The talks are prepared and given by Christadelphians&mdash;people who try to follow Christ and who look to Scripture as the guide for belief and life.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="bright-section bright-section--who-video" aria-labelledby="who-title">
  <div class="container about-who-video">
    <div class="about-who-video__text">
      <header class="bright-section__head about-who-video__head">
        <h2 id="who-title">Who are we?</h2>
        <p class="bright-lead">
          The name <em>Christadelphian</em> comes from Greek and means &ldquo;brothers in Christ.&rdquo;
          Christadelphians aim to follow the good news Jesus taught and lived, using the Bible as the authority for faith and practice&mdash;the same hope the apostles spoke of as the hope of Israel.
        </p>
      </header>
    </div>
    <div class="about-who-video__media">
      <h3 class="about-who-video__video-heading" id="video-overview-title">Video overview</h3>
      <p class="bright-muted about-who-video__video-lead">
        A short introduction to who we are and what we care about.
      </p>
      {% if youtubeVideoId %}
        <div class="bright-video">
          <div class="bright-video__embed">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/{{ youtubeVideoId }}"
              title="Overview of the Christadelphians"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              allowfullscreen
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        <div class="bright-video-fallback">
          <p>
            Watch introductions and studies on
            <a href="https://christadelphianvideo.org/who-are-the-christadelphians/">ChristadelphianVideo.org</a>
            &mdash; including material on who Christadelphians are and what they stand for.
          </p>
          <a class="btn btn--bright-primary" href="https://christadelphianvideo.org/who-are-the-christadelphians/">Open ChristadelphianVideo.org</a>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% set transcriptHref = transcriptUrl if transcriptUrl else (("/transcripts/" ~ transcriptSlug ~ "/") if transcriptSlug else "") %}
      {% if transcriptHref %}
        <p class="about-who-video__transcript">
          <a class="about-who-video__transcript-link" href="{{ transcriptHref }}">Read the transcript</a>
        </p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="about-bottom-cta">
  <button type="button" class="btn btn--bright-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/christadelphians/'">Learn More About the Christadelphians</button>
</div>